  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK730">
<l>uḷareṉiṉu millārō ṭoppar kaḷaṉañcik</l>
<l>kaṟṟa celaccollā tār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who through fear of the assembly are unable to set forth their learning in an interesting manner, though alive, are yet like the dead.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
